OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784489755
OL,3,CRussia launches one of its biggest
OL,4,Cballistic missile attacks on Kyiv
OL,6,FRussia launched one its largest
OL,7,Fballistic attacks since its full-scale
OL,8,Finvasion of Ukraine in 2022 overnight
OL,9,Finto Sunday, according to Kyiv
OL,10,Fauthorities.
OL,12,FOne person was killed and a further 16
OL,13,Finjured.
OL,15,FUkraine's air force said Moscow had
OL,16,Flaunched "a massive combined strike
OL,17,Fagainst Ukraine using attack UAVs and
OL,18,Fvarious types of air- and ground-
OL,19,Flaunched missiles" and that the main
OL,20,Ftarget had been the capital.
OL,26,@xD@JOU{D@RO]
