OL,3,CRussia launches one of its biggest
OL,4,Cballistic missile attacks on Kyiv
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe attack began around 1:30am local
OL,12,Ftime and lasted several hours, causing
OL,13,Fexplosions across the capital and
OL,14,Fsparking fires in five districts.
OL,16,FUkraine's State Emergency Service said
OL,17,Frescue workers pulled people from
OL,18,Fburning structures in the
OL,19,FSviatoshynskyi and Shevchenkivskyi
OL,20,Fdistricts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
