CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784489755
OL,3,CRussia launches one of its biggest
OL,4,Cballistic missile attacks on Kyiv
OL,6,F"The enemy launched more than 40
OL,7,Fmissiles of various types ` most of
OL,8,Fthem against the capital ` and 120
OL,9,Fattack drones," President Volodymyr
OL,10,FZelenskyy said.
OL,12,FAir defences had "shot down or
OL,13,Fneutralised 126 targets, including 18
OL,14,Fmissiles and 108 unmanned aerial
OL,15,Fvehicles," the air force said.
OL,17,FMoscow said the attack targeted sites
OL,18,Flinked to the Ukrainian military.
