OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784489755
OL,3,CRussia launches one of its biggest
OL,4,Cballistic missile attacks on Kyiv
OL,6,FRussia has launched several large-
OL,7,Fscale attacks on Kyiv in recent weeks
OL,8,Fas Ukraine faces a shortage of Patriot
OL,9,Fair defence missiles, which are its
OL,10,Fmost effective means of intercepting
OL,11,FRussian ballistic missiles.
OL,13,FUS President Donald Trump has said he
OL,14,Fis prepared to grant Ukraine licenses
OL,15,Fto produce Patriot interceptor
OL,16,Fmissiles, potentially bolstering
OL,17,FKyiv's defenses against Russian
OL,18,Fballistic missile attacks. However,
OL,19,Fthe details and timeline for
OL,20,Fimplementing the decision remain
OL,21,Funclear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
